name: Geo_Type
desc: This field specifies the geographic resolution of the match type and holds one of the following values

values.name: COUNTRY
values.desc: match was at the country level

values.name: USSTATE
values.desc: match was to a US state

values.name: USCITY
values.desc: match was to a US city or landmark

values.name: WORLDCITY
values.desc: match was to a city or landmark outside the US

values.name: WORLDSTATE
values.desc: match was to an Administrative Division 1 outside the US â€“ roughly equivalent to a US state
